  * debian/xulrunner-dev.preinst.in: Add a preinst script to remove
    /usr/lib/xulrunner-devel-GRE_VERSION/sdk/bin before upgrading from versions
    <= 5.0-2. Closes: #634053.
  * debian/control*:
